    "What are the performance gaps in the industry?": "Many security professionals struggle with consistently identifying subtle indicators of potential threats. Recognizing these early warning signs is crucial for proactive security measures. Without a keen eye for detail and an understanding of potential threat behaviors, vulnerabilities may go unnoticed until it's too late, leading to security breaches and compromised safety.",
