    "Why do you think this WSQ course will address the training needs for the industry?": "The course trains security teams to collaborate and use methods of risk analysis, this improves their ability to make well informed recommendations. Professionals will learn how to assess the situation and identify risks, this ensures resources are allocated where they are most needed, significantly strengthening overall protection."
  }
]
